Aloha!

Our team is looking to get some spare 1/16" walled 1.5" and 2" box tubing for our thrifty telescope while we are in the Greater Los Angeles/Southern California regiona for OCR. (We are pretty sure we dented one of the tubes which is causing significant binding.) OnlineMetals unfortunately says it’s now discontinued (that’s where we originally got it). Are there any local vendors anyone knows of that we could contact to get the stock?

Mahalo in advance for leads!
